name: Tynker Junior - Visual Coding for Pre-Readers
description: Visual block-based coding for ages 5-7 using pre-reader friendly interface. Learn sequencing, loops, and problem-solving through interactive games and puzzles.

name: Tynker Block Coding - Grades 2-5
description: Drag-and-drop block coding covering fundamental programming concepts. Create games, animations, and interactive stories while learning variables, conditionals, and loops.

name: Tynker Python Introduction
description: Transition from block coding to Python text-based programming. Learn Python syntax, data structures, and algorithms through guided projects and challenges.

name: Tynker JavaScript Fundamentals
description: Learn JavaScript for web development and interactive applications. Build websites, games, and projects while mastering modern web programming.

name: Tynker Game Design Course
description: Comprehensive game design course teaching gameplay mechanics, level design, and programming. Create platformers, adventure games, and multiplayer experiences.

name: Tynker Minecraft Coding
description: Learn coding through Minecraft modding and world creation. Program custom behaviors, build automated structures, and create mini-games within Minecraft.

name: Tynker Mobile App Development
description: Design and build mobile apps for iOS and Android. Learn UI design, event handling, and data management while creating functional mobile applications.
stem_fields: Computer Science, Mobile Development, App Design

name: Tynker Advanced Python Programming
description: Advanced Python course covering object-oriented programming, data structures, algorithms, and libraries. Build complex projects and prepare for AP Computer Science.

name: Tynker Data Science & AI
description: Introduction to data science and artificial intelligence for teens. Learn data analysis, machine learning basics, and build AI-powered projects with Python.

name: Tynker Web Development Course
description: Full-stack web development covering HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and backend basics. Build responsive websites, web apps, and interactive experiences.

name: Tynker Robotics & Drones
description: Program drones and robots using visual and text-based coding. Learn about sensors, actuators, and autonomous systems through virtual simulations.

name: Tynker AR/VR Development
description: Create augmented and virtual reality experiences. Learn 3D programming, spatial design, and immersive technology development.

name: Tynker AP Computer Science Prep
description: Comprehensive preparation for AP Computer Science A exam. Covers Java programming, algorithms, data structures, and problem-solving aligned with College Board curriculum.

name: Tynker Creative Arts & Coding
description: Combine art and programming to create digital animations, interactive art, and generative designs. Learn creative coding with Processing and p5.js.

name: Tynker Music & Sound Programming
description: Create music and sound effects through code. Learn music theory basics, sound synthesis, and build interactive musical instruments and compositions.

name: Tynker Math & Coding Integration
description: Learn mathematics through coding projects. Visualize algebra, geometry, and statistics concepts while building interactive math games and simulations.

name: Tynker Physics & Simulation
description: Build physics simulations and learn scientific concepts through code. Create gravity simulations, collision detection, and interactive physics experiments.

name: Tynker Storytelling & Animation
description: Create animated stories and interactive narratives. Learn character animation, scene design, and storytelling techniques through code.

name: Tynker Puzzle & Logic Games
description: Design puzzle and logic games while learning computational thinking. Create brain teasers, escape rooms, and strategy games with coding.

name: Tynker Multiplayer Game Development
description: Build online multiplayer games with real-time interaction. Learn networking concepts, server-client architecture, and collaborative gameplay design.

name: Tynker Coding for Educators
description: Comprehensive classroom curriculum and resources for teachers. Includes lesson plans, assessment tools, and student progress tracking for K-12 coding education.

name: Tynker Summer Coding Camp - Game Dev
description: Week-long online summer camp focused on game development. Create multiple games using block coding and text-based programming with live instruction.

name: Tynker Summer Coding Camp - Python
description: Intensive week-long Python programming camp for beginners and intermediate students. Build projects, learn syntax, and develop problem-solving skills with live instructors.

name: Tynker Summer Coding Camp - Minecraft
description: Learn coding through Minecraft modding and world creation. Week-long camp teaching programming fundamentals with popular gaming platform.

name: Tynker Summer Coding Camp - Mobile Apps
description: Design and develop mobile applications in this week-long intensive camp. Learn UI design, app logic, and deployment with experienced instructors.
stem_fields: Mobile Development, Computer Science, App Design

name: Tynker Certificate Programs
description: Earn coding certificates by completing structured learning paths. Demonstrate proficiency in various programming languages and concepts with shareable credentials.
